The Orbited plugin enables "real time" updates using Orbited + STOMP

See:
* https://pypi.python.org/pypi/orbited
* https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Streaming_Text_Oriented_Messaging_Protocol

Installation
============
add "addModule('Orbited');"
to the bottom of your config.php

Settings
========
webserver:
webport:
channelbase:
stompserver:
stompport:
username:
password:
webuser:
webpass:

Example
=======
addModule('Orbited', array(
    'webserver' => '',
    'webport' => '',
    'channelbase' => '',
    'stompserver' => '',
    'stompport' => '',
    'username' => '',
    'password' => '',
    'webuser' => '',
    'webpass' => ''
));

